description:
Brooke and Danielle are joined by TikToker Jenna Palek!  The gals discuss Jenna’s impressive and eventful last year with her growth on TikTok, her viral resume, moving to Austin and starting a new life post-grad.  Jenna shares more about her current role at TikTok, being a creator, college tips, career tips and so much more.
